### ─── WHATSAPP MCP ────────────────────────────────

### WhatsApp - Get Message History
POST http://localhost:6060/whatsapp/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "917796449253",
  "limit": 10
}


### WhatsApp - Send a Message
POST http://localhost:6060/whatsapp/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "917796449253",
  "message": "Hello from OmniChannel MCP test",
  "customerId": "test_001"
}


### WhatsApp - Broadcast
POST http://localhost:6060/whatsapp/broadcast
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerIds": ["PUT_REAL_MONGO_ID_HERE"],
  "message": "Your issue has been resolved. Thank you for your patience.",
  "campaignName": "test_broadcast_march_2026"
}


