### LinkedIn - Get Brand Comments
POST http://localhost:6060/linkedin/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brandName": "HDFC Bank",
  "keyword": "complaint",
  "limit": 10
}


### ─── TWITTER MCP ─────────────────────────────────

### Twitter - Search Complaints
POST http://localhost:6060/twitter/complaints
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "keyword": "complaint",
  "brandName": "HDFC Bank",
  "limit": 15
}


### Twitter - Search Fraud/Scam
